Package net.proteusframework.core.gson

Select Gson Extras.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EnhancedJsonAdapter
    Can be implemented by type adapters registered via JsonAdapter in combination with ContextJsonAdapterAnnotationTypeAdapterFactory.
    GsonHelper
    Provides helper methods and objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnySubclassTypeAdapterFactory<T>
    Adapts values whose runtime type may differ from their declaration type.
    AnySubclassTypeAdapterFactory.Any
    Any class for array capturing and replacement of using Object.class.
    ContextJsonAdapterAnnotationTypeAdapterFactory
    Given a type T, looks for the annotation JsonAdapter and uses an instance of the specified class as the default type adapter and check if it is an EnhancedJsonAdapter.
    GsonHelperImpl
    Helper implementation.
    HibernateHelper
    Workaround to avoid pulling in more dependencies to core-processor.jar.
    PostConstructAdapterFactory
    The type Post construct adapter factory.
    PostConstructAdapterFactory.PostConstructAdapter<T>  
    RuntimeTypeAdapterFactory<T>
    Adapts values whose runtime type may differ from their declaration type.
    TimeZoneAdapter
    TimeZone Adapter.
